scene.message:
Nanjo: There was something{nl}
striking, almost lifelike,{nl}
in Sonomura's painting that{nl}
I saw.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Oh yeah, she was good{nl}
at painting, huh...{wait_fr:32} {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
C'mon, let's get to the{nl}
hospital!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I've seen Sonomura's{nl}
painting too.{wait_fr:32} It won a prize,{nl}
titled "Gate of Paradise."{waitkey}{ret}

Student: We're short on{nl}
members, it's a real pain.{nl}
Sonomura's hospitalized, and{nl}
Kozai won't come to school.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Do you know about{nl}
those two?{waitkey}{nl}
{ctl0e:2}{ret}

Student: Sonomura's paintings{nl}
are amazing. She's won lots{nl}
of prizes.{waitkey}Her best friend Kozai was{nl}
hopeless at painting, but{nl}
when it came to boyfriends,{nl}
she seemed to win out.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Oh, you don't know.{nl}
Yeah, the art club's just had{nl}
one hardship after another.{nl}
Maybe we're even cursed.{waitkey}{ret}
